<div class="title">A Godsend</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Chris&Exact=1">Chris</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Chris. "A Godsend: An Experience with Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp18367)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 24, 2002. erowid.org/exp/18367</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

